<abstract><t>BGP has been used as the routing protocol in many hyper-scale data centers.  This document proposes a BGP neighbor autodiscovery mechanism that greatly simplifies BGP deployments.  This mechanism is very useful for those hyper-scale data centers where BGP is used as the routing protocol.</t></abstract>

